==Description==
The '''Greatball''' is a type of [[Pokéballs|Pokéball]]. It automatically tries to catch a wild Pokémon after defeating it if is the highest type of Pokéball active and there is a remaining supply in the Pokéball selector.

==Details==
A better Pokéball to capture Pokémon with, it provides a +5% catch rate bonus and catches Pokémon in 1 second.

